Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽一開始 發展就出乎意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一站 美國杯車賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領先前頭的是這次大賽中出道的菲爾．弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在預賽首日就以驚人圈速取得最優先位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在這場決賽中也成了他獨領風騷的局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連第二位的隊友加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已經被拋離到40秒以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!這樣一開始就變得不是在賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹甚麼!慢了一整圈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 我不是為了讓人超車而比賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人和...這位...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車號7號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落之環的雷歐．安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見果然很急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡和慢一圈的車子相撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒霉透頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我第一場比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 迎接的準備做好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.20,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頒獎典禮和後來的採訪是逃避不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾得做好這個工作才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AL-ZARD現在接受揮舞的方格子旗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼從容的勝利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾．弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出道就拿下第一優先位置和勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼蘭德爾之後史上第二個創下此快舉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們爭奪前頭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有互相信任對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才可能做到極限邊緣的競爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你這今天才出道一下子就想模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不可能成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣跑法有危險的不只你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人也可能遭到波及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.80,0:04:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點道理你該知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 風見 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的事我代他向你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向我道歉是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常瞭解 可是也別太過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被媒體知道了就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好教訓他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還想讓他在下一場車賽跑的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.90,0:04:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死人了!那算甚麼態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個新人罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.60,0:05:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 有點受寵若驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好像成了電影明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們之前從來沒透露任何信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是連弗利茲的聲音也沒聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是賽車前驚動大家沒什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人在出道前都是很緊張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再施加壓力上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往往就無法發揮出實力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那即是說 你們一開始就知道他會優勝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我們和AL-ZARD存在的作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 名雲社長你一開始就看好弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是加賀嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上現在加賀只跑到第五名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒那個打轉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他或許會得第二名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣 他和菲爾還是差很遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆的車子在外觀上有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的只是外觀嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的自動系統也有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AL-ZARD是以有機物質為介質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採用了生化電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生疏一點的人很難駕駛它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.80,0:06:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以加賀的車子裡採用的是舊有的開發系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括稀有金屬變型系統也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我期待菲爾的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本來就是這部車的測試員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以非常熟練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.40,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是我認為加賀能力不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利茲先生\N請問你駕駛閃電霹靂車有何感受？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是要在這地方睡著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那位女性有問題問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你參加閃電霹靂車有何感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和風見先生...古德利安先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一賽車場上比賽...我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下次能和他們兩人較量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也要等他們兩人追上你的車才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的難以置信呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那斯卡車賽一直是墊底的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表示他很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼講太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 是誰在這地方亂扔垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.10,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為誰擁有足夠跟風見和古德利安競賽的技術？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是為了在前頭接受方格旗揮舞而存在的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.80,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出我才不在乎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走著瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一場我就是優勝者!冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也算閃電霹靂車的車手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過「猴子的屁股笑話」嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股笑話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是日本的諺語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自己的屁股也是紅色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻笑其它的猴子的紅屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為那和現在的你很貼切呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 對方看來較年輕更受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼晚去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先一步回德國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為我不在就做出脫軌行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就走?那邊已經是深夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想在下一站也有同樣的遭遇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要從速採取應變措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然以後哪一個車隊都會變得難對付起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你看來被甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回房睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別去了 風見先生已經很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他比賽被迫退出 心情好像非常不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會挨罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才要更努力安慰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆在房裡太無聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩他不在房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了 安利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.50,0:10:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...風見先生去哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 總之他不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有甚麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩哪有時間理你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.50,0:11:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我做了個防止退場的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.00,0:11:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希爾結果通宵完成報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翌日就第一個拿著報告去道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他那樣終於被原諒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.30,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家說那個教授不會那樣子就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次輪到他發難就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想著已經結束了的車賽沒有用的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.00,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 車賽才剛剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.50,0:11:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的焦躁是今天車賽引起的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白退場使你很不甘心 但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳甚麼都不知道就不要多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你們在這裡約會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都變成大人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 你一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一個人 很可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.30,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話 一起好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以妨礙你們難得的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 腦中全是賽車的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真像你的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎?想著賽車的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒有說不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在再怎麼想也無濟於事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.90,0:12:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 賽車是快的人獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說美貴和新條來了美國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 算是修行之旅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也真有趣 有那種想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貴好有勇氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 想想我還真是羨慕新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想像他那樣比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀你不是很幸運嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開那麼快的賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有了那種跑車要優勝也決不是做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想開速度快的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以到葵車隊來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肯替我付毀約的賠償金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隨時都可以不幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.20,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管那是不是什麼最新科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那種感覺惡劣的賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前從未駕駛過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你願意替我開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺惡劣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:14:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那車子設計時是完全不考慮賽車手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是追求快速 再快速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我漸漸不知道是我在駕駛它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是它載著我來參加賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.50,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一直講求速度下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就會演變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是討厭坐在那樣的車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 話題變得濃重起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是暫時無法和這傢伙見面了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不!不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不是在做車子的性能比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有同等的力量的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不像是賽車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了 一開幕就兩連勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都是遙遙領先地衝線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是名雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要被速度快的車子載著跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝出是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 但是妳以前沒那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有和多年奮鬥的工作人員一起努力勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這次竟然連車手在內撤換了一半工作人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的車隊並非真正的葵車隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法達到目的的人被淘汰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.30,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也知道 但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是將來要領導葵財團的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要有那種天真的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要給妳找個理想的對象才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 那件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如 像名雲那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和會長都覺得他不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.10,0:16:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是名雲 我應該可以把葵的將來交託給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是時候要認真考慮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好妳跟名雲的年紀相當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會和那種人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 妳總是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是爸爸不會容許妳任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳選擇丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.80,0:17:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在選擇葵將來的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}第三站 加拿大杯 加斯帕湖賽車道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.70,0:17:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續三站都要退出 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.60,0:17:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 力量汽缸改為 0.82吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後磁石離合器呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換掉變檔控制器和氣壓傳動裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.00,0:17:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見進入工作站已經超過30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情形看來很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能回來賽車場嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打電話詢問的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作人員不打電話問就連維修都做不好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蕾雅小姐也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道她在日本做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連賽車場都不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.90,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 風見下車了 他退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近狀態不振的風見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼第一站後今站再度以退出結束比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你說得太過分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不像克蕾雅小姐般了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但良平也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽中結果就等於一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有努力是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 妳到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正現在返回賽道也無法勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑也是白跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是以前的隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對不會說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過無論任何時候機會是一定會有的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我說教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有獲勝的可能性還另當別論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為拿一分兩分有屁用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 說獲勝不代表一切的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是明日香妳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的男朋友沒拿到優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不高興嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人...你那樣說...太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法 這次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我怎樣努力都拿不到優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.40,0:19:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄這場比賽在下次比賽拿分數比較…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.40,0:19:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷 你又說出沒出息的話來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.10,0:19:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德爾 你別偷聽我們說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你先大吼大叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.50,0:20:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這就是最近你比賽自暴自棄的原因嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的老毛病又犯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把贏不了的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推托在其他人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭德爾!別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說 你有辦法贏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.80,0:20:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏那輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再厲害也贏不了那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.00,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不是抱著你那種心情參加比賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點在成績上已經表現得很清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 受不了你這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是11的冠軍 打敗我的男人的模樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 不要連明日香妳也令我心情煩躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳只懂說那些話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就別到賽車場來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.78,0:21:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}第四站 法國杯站 薩爾德賽車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就位前10分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.80,0:21:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請還在車位上的工作人員馬上離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.10,0:21:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請還在車位上的工作人員馬上離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是喜歡賽車場呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.70,0:21:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實妳不必親自過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經按照指示完成在日本的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.00,0:21:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 我來這裡會妨礙到你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 絕對不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常歡迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.70,0:21:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.20,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟我說了一件敏感的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.90,0:22:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你老實回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對葵財團的社長寶座有興趣是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.70,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.30,0:22:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不相信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.00,0:22:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很自負我是\N足以創造和葵財團相匹敵的企業的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必依賴女人的財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.60,0:22:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.50,0:22:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那並非因為妳是葵財團的繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.80,0:22:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著因為背負著葵財團而擺出那樣的防備姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有葵集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也十分有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好看清我這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到妳能相信我的話是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四站 法國杯站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.80,0:23:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞過一圈後 又呈現出大家熟悉的情景了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.10,0:23:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第一位置起跑的弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.10,0:23:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始和排第二位的加賀拉大差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.90,0:23:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果勝出這一站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.90,0:23:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於開幕後連贏四場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.70,0:23:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就平了2017年風見創下的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.80,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是以前的隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.90,0:23:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.80,0:23:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過無論任何時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定會有機會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.50,0:23:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我沒有抱著你那種心情參賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.10,0:23:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們要我怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大飯桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.70,0:24:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連起跑時的搖動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.80,0:24:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線車道的加速沒有過失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.60,0:24:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼時候都正確冷靜地跑在記錄線上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.00,0:24:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事真的可能嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.20,0:24:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.80,0:24:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想沒問題 已經進入這邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.70,0:24:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.20,0:24:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進入掃瞄室 以後再檢查車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.40,0:25:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快備份資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.80,0:25:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除B系統的主程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.60,0:25:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關上貨櫃艙口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.60,0:25:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再注射一支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.00,0:25:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果大量注射中和劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.60,0:25:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了!注射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.30,0:25:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去什麼都做不成 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.90,0:25:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.30,0:25:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利茲的退出令比賽變得不明朗
